'''Sungweh (Songwee) Afahyɛ''' afehyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfoɔ a wɔn wɔ Sampa-Jaman wɔ Bono Mantam mu a ɛyɛ kane Bono ne Ahafo Manatam wɔ Ghana no di. Wodi saa afahyɛ yi wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so nsɔn no mu<ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref><ref>https://www.nhoc.gov.gh/festivals</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔde nnuane ne nsa gye ahohoɔ wɔ afahyɛ no ase. Amanfoɔ no hyɛ wɔn amammerɛ ntadeɛ ahorɔw de kɔ dwa dataa a ahenfo no abɔ no ase. Asa ne nnwomtoɔ nso kɔ so wɔ afahyɛ no ase<ref>http://www.ghanaembassyiran.com/en/page/majorfestivals</ref>

== Mfasoɔ ==
Wodi saa afahyɛ yi de kae nneɛma bi a esii wɔ tete<ref>https://www.ghanaconsulatedubai.com/tourism.html</ref>

